Name: Pythonol
Version: 2.1
Release: 1
Copyright: Erica Andrews (PhrozenSmoke@yahoo.com)
Group: Educational
Vendor: Phrozen Smoke
Url: http://pythonol.sourceforge.net
Provides: PyBabelPhish,pybabelphish,pybabelfish,PyBabelFish,Pythonol,pythonol
Requires: python >= 2.2,pygtk >= 1.99,gtk+ >= 2.0.0 ,/usr/bin/env

%description
A Gtk-based full-featured Spanish-English educational suite for Linux. Features include a Spanish-English dictionary, a Spanish-English thesaurus, Idioms, full-text translations, vocabulary quizzes, verb conjugation (28 different tenses), and text-to-speech support so words can be read aloud in Spanish. Pythonol 'talks'! This package does not include the Festival extension needed for text-to-speech support. 

